        "text_Y6hjLD": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>BEDGEAR wants you to have 100% of the comfort and support you need to get a great night’s sleep so you can Wake Ready each day with our Performance® bedding products. We want to make sure our bedding products live up to their intent. That’s why we have created a 365 Night Guaranty that goes well beyond any traditional bedding manufacturer’s warranty. We also have established a special 10-year warranty with our partner GM Warranty Services for customers who have purchased a mattress and mattress protector together.<\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p><strong>Mattress Purchased With a Mattress Protector – GM Warranty Services:<\/strong><\/p><p>Our 365 Night Guaranty is extended to a full 10 years from your date of delivery; all warranty restrictions apply.<br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/MP-gm-warranty.pdf?v=1745348436\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/MP-gm-warranty.pdf?v=1745348436\">GM Warranty (EN)<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Protectors_Sheets_Blankets_Warranty_12022020_FRENCH.pdf?v=1745349476\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Protectors_Sheets_Blankets_Warranty_12022020_FRENCH.pdf?v=1745349476\">GM Warranty (FR)<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/integration-5ojmyuq-nidg67ibnp6vg.us-3.magentosite.cloud\/media\/wysiwyg\/cms\/warranty\/en_US\/pdf\/PPT076-Dri-Tec-10yr-Warranty-13.6x10.9-spanish_3-27-17.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">GM Warranty (ES)<\/a><\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p><strong>Mattresses<\/strong><\/p><p>Our 365 Night Guaranty is extended to a full 10 years from your date of delivery; all warranty restrictions apply.<br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Mattress_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745348623\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Mattress_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745348623\">Mattress Warranty (EN)<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Mattress_Warranty_06152020_FRENCH.pdf?v=1745349476\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Mattress_Warranty_06152020_FRENCH.pdf?v=1745349476\">Mattress Warranty (FR)<\/a><\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p><strong>M3 Mattress Guaranty:<\/strong><\/p><p>Our 365 Night Guaranty is extended to a full 10 years from your date of delivery; all warranty restrictions apply.<br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_M3_Mattress_Warranty_Final_04182023.pdf?v=1745348623\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_M3_Mattress_Warranty_Final_04182023.pdf?v=1745348623\">M3 Mattress Warranty (EN)<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_M3_Mattress_Warranty_Final_04182023_fr_FR_ver.pdf?v=1745349476\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_M3_Mattress_Warranty_Final_04182023_fr_FR_ver.pdf?v=1745349476\">M3 Mattress Warranty (FR)<\/a><\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p><strong>Kids Mattresses Guaranty:<\/strong><\/p><p>Our 365 Night Guaranty is extended to a full 10 years from your date of delivery; all warranty restrictions apply.<br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Kids_Mattress_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745348623\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Kids_Mattress_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745348623\">Kids Mattress Warranty<\/a><\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p><strong>Crib Mattresses Guaranty:<\/strong><\/p><p>Our 365 Night Guaranty includes only our crib mattress covers. We feature a limited lifetime warranty on our crib mattress cores.<br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/integration-5ojmyuq-nidg67ibnp6vg.us-3.magentosite.cloud\/media\/wysiwyg\/cms\/warranty\/en_US\/pdf\/BEDGEAR_Crib_Mattress_06152020.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Crib Mattress Warranty<\/a><\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p><strong>Adjustable Bases Guaranty:<\/strong><\/p><p>Our 365 Night Guaranty is extended to a full 3 years from your date of delivery; all warranty restrictions apply.<br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Adjustable_Base_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745336122\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Adjustable_Base_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745336122\">Adjustable Base Warranty (EN)<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Adjustable_Base_Warranty_06152020_FRENCH.pdf?v=1745349476\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Adjustable_Base_Warranty_06152020_FRENCH.pdf?v=1745349476\">Adjustable Base Warranty (FR)<\/a><\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p><strong>Pillows Guaranty:<\/strong><\/p><p>Our 365 Night Guaranty includes all our Performance pillows; all warranty restrictions apply.<br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Pillows_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745348624\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Pillows_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745348624\">Pillows Warranty (EN)<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Pillows_Warranty_06152020_FRENCH.pdf?v=1745349476\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Pillows_Warranty_06152020_FRENCH.pdf?v=1745349476\">Pillows Warranty (FR)<\/a><\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p><strong>Mattress Protectors, Sheets and Blankets Guaranty:<\/strong><\/p><p>Our 365 Night Guaranty features a limited warranty.<br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Protectors_Sheets_Blankets_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745348624\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Protectors_Sheets_Blankets_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745348624\">Mattress Protectors, Sheets and Blankets Warranty (EN)<\/a> | <a href=\"https:\/\/integration-5ojmyuq-nidg67ibnp6vg.us-3.magentosite.cloud\/media\/wysiwyg\/cms\/warranty\/en_US\/pdf\/BEDGEAR_Protectors_Sheets_Blankets_Warranty_12022020_FRENCH.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Mattress Protectors, Sheets and Blankets Warranty (FR)<\/a><\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p><strong>Pet Beds Guaranty:<\/strong><\/p><p>Our 365 Night Guaranty features a limited warranty.<br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Pet_Beds_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745348624\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0672\/6890\/3052\/files\/BEDGEAR_Pet_Beds_Warranty_09032024.pdf?v=1745348624\">Pet Beds Warranty<\/a><\/p><p><br\/><\/p><p><strong>CONTACT US<\/strong><\/p><p>Please contact us at wow@bedgear.com or 631-414-7763 for assistance.<br\/>BEDGEAR, LLC<br\/>200 Sea Lane<br\/>Farmingdale, NY 11735<\/p><p>Contact GM Warranty Services at <a href=\"tel:1-800-545-7125\">(800) 545-7125<\/a> or visit <a href=\"https:\/\/bedgear.com\/pages\/warranty-landing\" title=\"https:\/\/bedgear.com\/pages\/warranty-landing\">http:\/\/www.gmwarrantyservices.com<\/a> to complete the contact form<\/p>"
          }
        }
